{"tid":1558456,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廿人太子站摧花　旺角揮利器兇記者　有記者被圍毆受傷","createTime":"2019-09-10T12:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T12:51:11.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac533b30116cde732800b47491f88acf3716ecb1","tid":1558456,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3263952/org/fde8554b48ed4feb02780b8a51cbcb31.jpg/ZZ7G-ChqonFbjxGdIsN1mBbvtGIk8bq8_18pecVfKXk?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3263952%2Forg%2Ffde8554b48ed4feb02780b8a51cbcb31.jpg%2FZZ7G-ChqonFbjxGdIsN1mBbvtGIk8bq8_18pecVfKXk%3Fv%3Dw800&h=1a8fa2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31港鐵太子站襲擊事件後，連日來均有市民在太子站外，擺放鮮花。凌晨4時許，約有20名「大媽」及一兩名男子，到港鐵太子站外，拆除市民近日放置在站外的鮮花。及至清晨約5時，該批男女步行至碧街與洗衣街交界「連儂牆」，有人用𠝹刀及油漆鏟清除牆上的紙張。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3263953/org/58fdf5b3aa66787f3a2b4736b8ed852b.jpg/iTxva5kMZfUy5a_BW4osylbN_IApYlbcx4NX8v2DV_I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3263953%2Forg%2F58fdf5b3aa66787f3a2b4736b8ed852b.jpg%2FiTxva5kMZfUy5a_BW4osylbN_IApYlbcx4NX8v2DV_I&h=c784dc69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n期間一名男記者聞訊，到場了解拍攝，突遭上述多名男女追打，並在旺角道近通菜街，將該名男記者推跌圍毆，致記者手部受傷。此時，數名其他傳媒的記者到場，立即喝止，其中一名「大媽」向《香港01》記者揮舞油漆鏟，記者閃避時撞傷腳部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3263949/org/bafdaa8d66d90ac4d43cac5b3798ade1.jpg/AIDt79ZF7hMtt-Pr_wWMw3rkdgEc0S8qbnLkxkRy5MY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3263949%2Forg%2Fbafdaa8d66d90ac4d43cac5b3798ade1.jpg%2FAIDt79ZF7hMtt-Pr_wWMw3rkdgEc0S8qbnLkxkRy5MY&h=6a714ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一眾狂徒隨即四散，有在場記者報警。現場消息稱，其中一名「大媽」曾截乘的士企圖離開，被記者追及，將的士截停，並交予到場警員處理。該名大媽一度被要求登上警車協助調查，據知有人曾從身上跌出一把剪刀。至於被圍毆的男記者，則向警方講述事發經過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3263951/org/7441fa9db29e7155306cf50ba912c345.jpg/GMOO2kfJ00LUlzVezzj0LQI-ymL_lIHVUBj483oY-PM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3263951%2Forg%2F7441fa9db29e7155306cf50ba912c345.jpg%2FGMOO2kfJ00LUlzVezzj0LQI-ymL_lIHVUBj483oY-PM&h=e05a1d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3263964/org/f57afb07ebdc656c2be1de1fc5261e2d.jpg/IOg545gYq6fNd71WeEVMA71MI1VBNMCTF9rVsT3a1bE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3263964%2Forg%2Ff57afb07ebdc656c2be1de1fc5261e2d.jpg%2FIOg545gYq6fNd71WeEVMA71MI1VBNMCTF9rVsT3a1bE&h=420dac99&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}